## Prompt Categories

### Joke Construction (Prompts 1-3, 9, 15)
The core engines for building individual comedy structures. Start with `skewed-perspective-generator` for quick wins, `one-liner-forge` for polished standalone jokes, `comedic-word-surgeon` for final word-level refinement.

### Content Engineering (Prompts 4-7, 10-11)
Layer comedy mechanics into longer-form content. `tension-release-writer` for story arcs, `comedy-hook-generator` for first-line engagement, `naming-the-unnamed` for brand-defining vocabulary moments.

### Strategy & Calibration (Prompts 8, 13, 16)
Audience and context alignment. `audience-calibrator` before any deployment, `comedy-content-adapter` for cross-vertical translation.

### Creative Process (Prompts 12, 14)
Ideation and meta-creative tools. `observation-to-bit-pipeline` for daily comedy intake, `meta-humor-engine` for self-aware brand moments.

### Specific ‚Üí Universal Mastery (Prompts 17-20)
The golden key: take something specific and make it universally understandable, applicable, engaging, and shareable. `specific-to-universal-bridge` for the core mechanic, `universal-resonance-amplifier` to upgrade existing niche content, `niche-to-viral-translator` to break expertise out of its bubble, `conversation-mastery-engine` to engineer content people MUST respond to.

## Workflow Decision Tree

**Start here**: What stage are you at?

- **"I have a raw observation"** ‚Üí `observation-to-bit-pipeline` ‚Üí `comedy-filter-stack`
- **"I need a hook/one-liner fast"** ‚Üí `comedy-hook-generator` or `one-liner-forge`
- **"I have content that's too flat"** ‚Üí `vivid-specificity-injector` ‚Üí `comedic-word-surgeon`
- **"I want to name a phenomenon"** ‚Üí `naming-the-unnamed`
- **"I need a structured comedic bit"** ‚Üí `rule-of-three-engine` or `bait-switch-architect`
- **"I'm writing for an unfamiliar audience"** ‚Üí `audience-calibrator` first
- **"I want to add humor to existing content"** ‚Üí `comedy-content-adapter`
- **"I need a tension-based story/hook"** ‚Üí `tension-release-writer`
- **"I want self-aware brand personality"** ‚Üí `meta-humor-engine`
- **"I need instant human connection"** ‚Üí `self-deprecation-connector`
- **"I want to take something niche and make it universal"** ‚Üí `specific-to-universal-bridge`
- **"My content only resonates with insiders"** ‚Üí `universal-resonance-amplifier`
- **"I want expert content to go viral"** ‚Üí `niche-to-viral-translator`
- **"I want people to HAVE to comment"** ‚Üí `conversation-mastery-engine`

## Quick Start

- **Immediate win**: Run `comedy-hook-generator` on your next 3 social posts
- **Daily practice**: Run `observation-to-bit-pipeline` every morning for a week
- **Content upgrade**: Run `comedy-content-adapter` on your best-performing post to make it funnier
- **Brand voice**: Run `naming-the-unnamed` on 3 experiences your audience shares but can't articulate

